fields.name: Vinoperfect serum
fields.description: Both effective and ultra-gentle on the skin, the Brightening Anti-Dark Spot Serum corrects and prevents the appearance of spots for a more radiant complexion. It works on all types of spots (sun, acne, pregnancy, age) and is suitable for all skin types, including the most sensitive.

fields.name: M Perfect Cover BB Cream SPF42
fields.description: MISSHA’s multifunctional BB cream perfectly covers imperfections, evens out skin tone, and smooths fine lines. Ideal for daily use, it simplifies your skincare routine. The buildable formula offers light to medium coverage. It provides toning, moisturizing, and soothing action thanks to propylene glycol, hydrolyzed collagen, sodium hyaluronate, rosemary extract, and macadamia seed oil. The formula, with SPF 42 PA++, protects the skin from UVA and UVB rays. Available in the shade light beige.

fields.name: Clear Improvement Charcoal Mask
fields.description: This purifying charcoal mask unclogs pores, leaving the skin perfectly cleansed. It deeply purifies, absorbs toxins caused by environmental factors, and eliminates impurities.

fields.name: Cleanance Hydra Soothing cream
fields.description:
It is a soothing and moisturizing treatment specifically designed for skin dried out by acne medication.

Avène Eau Thermale Cleanance Hydra Soothing Cream helps restore skin comfort.

The Avène Thermal Spring Water in Cleanance Hydra Soothing Cream delivers all its soothing and softening properties.

Thanks to a key active ingredient, dextran sulfate, Cleanance Hydra Soothing Cream calms and reduces redness.

Its moisturizing and emollient ingredients help rebuild the altered hydrolipidic film to improve skin comfort.

Avène Eau Thermale Cleanance Hydra Soothing Cream is a rich, non-greasy cream that is easy to apply and quickly absorbed.

The skin is soothed and hydrated.

Thanks to Avène Eau Thermale Cleanance Hydra Soothing Cream, it is easier to continue your drying medication treatment regularly.

fields.name: Endocare gel cream
fields.description:
Formulated as a creamy, non-greasy gel, this product contains regenerating and antioxidant ingredients that help reduce visible signs of photoaging and accelerate skin regeneration after dermocosmetic treatments.

Enriched with SCA Biorepair Technology, a natural source of skin regeneration with antioxidant and reparative properties. Clinically proven effectiveness on stressed and photoaged skin.

fields.name: Sunbrella demi make-up SPF 30
fields.description: Sunscreen SPF 30 combines chemical and physical protection factors for optimal defense. Its chemical filters contribute to a lightweight, smooth texture, while zinc oxide, as a physical filter, offers protection and anti-inflammatory benefits. Ideal for breakout-prone skin, regular use of Sunbrella helps minimize imperfections. The matte finish is perfect for warm weather care, and its subtle tint evens out skin tone, eliminating the need for multiple products by providing coverage and protection in one step.

fields.name: Heliocare Age Active Fluid
fields.description:
Daily photoprotective treatment against signs of aging. It offers broad-spectrum protection and helps prevent and repair skin aging caused by sun exposure and other environmental stress factors.

Its innovative formulation creates an anti-pollution protective film, while its triple anti-aging complex (Hyaluronic Acid, Serine, Trehalose) helps reduce wrinkles and restore firmness.

Its broad-spectrum photoprotection helps prevent signs of aging caused by UVB, UVA, visible light, and IR-A. The presence of Fernblock®+ and glycosylase protects against the effects of oxidative stress and pollution, factors associated with skin aging processes.

fields.name: Soothing eye contour cream
fields.description:
This eye contour treatment has an emollient effect on sensitive eyelids and provides a soothing, lightweight sensation.

Its formula, enriched with moisturizing agents, protects the eye contour and eyelids. It soothes this delicate and fragile area, combats the feeling of tightness, and reduces redness around the eyes.

Rich in Avène Thermal Spring Water, the Soothing Eye Contour Treatment helps strengthen the skin barrier. Fragrance-free.

fields.name: Age Stellar Extra intense angi-age youth cream
fields.description: An extraordinary texture with a cotton-like touch and a warm, captivating fragrance. To act on wrinkles on four fronts: quantity width, dryness and depth. A formulation rich in high performing active ingredients to fight of skin aging.

fields.name: Firming eye cream
fields.description: Firming Eye Cream is designed to firm the skin, enhance hydration, and slow the appearance of aging signs around the eyes. It works to refine fine lines, improve elasticity, and strengthen the skin’s structure and function, addressing the unique challenges of this sensitive area.

fields.name: Airbrush Flawless Setting Spray
fields.description: This delicately scented, LONG-LASTING lightweight setting spray WEIGHTLESSLY sets the look of your makeup without melting, fading or settling into fine lines. Instantly lock in your look for makeup magic that looks ‘just applied’!

fields.name: Uniq One All in One Hair Treatment
fields.description:
Discover 10 benefits in a single product. Revlon Professional Uniq One All In One Classic provides a revitalizing treatment for all hair types. This revolutionary leave-in spray tackles nearly all hair concerns.

Plus, it leaves your hair with a captivating fragrance—starting with notes of pineapple, green apple, and pear, followed by a floral blend of peony, lily of the valley, patchouli, and orange blossom. The scent is perfectly finished with cedarwood and raspberry.

From now on, you won’t need dozens of hair care bottles in your bathroom—just one is enough!

fields.name: Cherry body cream
fields.description:
Nourish your skin with the expertise of Mario Fissi Laboratories. Mario Fissi Soothing Cherry Body Cream is a must-have for normal to dry skin.

Its rich texture is enhanced with cherry extract and shea butter, natural ingredients that nourish, soothe, and calm the skin.

Applied daily after a bath or shower, this body cream deeply nourishes the epidermis, leaving it soft, velvety, and delicately scented.

With a fully biodegradable formula and packaging that uses 50% less plastic, this product is also environmentally friendly.

fields.name: Cocoa Butter Body Cream
fields.description:
Nivea Cocoa Butter Body Cream is an extra-moisturizing treatment specially designed for dry skin.

Formulated with Intensive Hydration Serum, Cocoa Butter, and Vitamin E, this Nivea cream provides deep and nourishing hydration, giving the skin a natural glow and a smooth, soft feel.

This cream cares for your skin in five ways:
	•	Provides 48-hour intense hydration
	•	Leaves skin incredibly soft
	•	Protects against dehydration
	•	Deeply nourishes
	•	Instantly gives a healthy, radiant appearance

Treat yourself to a moment of relaxation—apply the cream daily, massaging it gently into your skin.

fields.name: Forever Glow styling oil
fields.description: The Pantene Pro-V Forever Glow Hair Oil protects against daily aggressors such as UV rays and humidity. Used after styling, this oil provides: 24-hour hold, strength, and shine, while nourishing the hair and helping to prevent split ends, ensuring a well-groomed look with strong, radiant hair.

fields.name: Irresistible
fields.description:
Irresistible Givenchy, a fragrance that invites you to let go.

The new Givenchy Irresistible Eau de Toilette celebrates feminine allure, blending a radiant rose with the softest musky woods.

Paired with iris and an exceptional blackcurrant bud, this irresistible rose is fruity, light, and ethereal.

Base notes of Virginia cedarwood and white musk enhance the bold femininity of this new Givenchy fragrance.

This Eau de Toilette is an invitation to surrender to a liberating dance and embrace the impulse to be yourself.

fields.name: Coconut Milk Anti breakage serum
fields.description: Strengthen & hydrate hair without weighing it down with this deeply nourishing anti-breakage hair serum. A tantalizing blend with coconut milk, coconut oil & egg white protein works to repair strands.

fields.name: Dry shampoo
fields.description:
Dry Shampoo with Rice Starch, known for its gentle emollient properties, refreshes and cleanses the hair without the need for water. Hair is instantly clean, revitalized, and regains its natural volume, as if freshly washed.

It absorbs excess oil and eliminates unwanted odors, leaving hair with a fresh, delicate fragrance.

No residue left behind.

fields.name: High Tech hair spray
fields.description:
Professional high-tech hairspray with an ideal evaporation rate to define movement and create volume.

It ensures shine and active hydration, making it perfect for all hairstyling techniques.

Neutral fragrance.
